## Day-2 Operations

```bash
# Detect manual changes in Azure (drift)
lzctl drift

# Verify state backend security posture (versioning, soft delete, TLS, encryption)
lzctl state health

# Create a named backup of all state files before a risky operation
lzctl state snapshot --all --tag "pre-maintenance-$(date +%Y%m%d)"

# Force-release a stuck blob lease after a failed pipeline
lzctl state unlock --key platform-connectivity.tfstate

# CAF compliance audit of the live Azure tenant
lzctl audit

# Check and apply AVM module version updates
lzctl upgrade
```
